        <Parent_String>siliceous sandstone [300011407], sandstone by composition: aggregate type [300011379], sandstone by composition or appearance [300157791], sandstone [300011376], sedimentary rock by composition [300011274], sedimentary rock [300011273], rock (inorganic material) [300011692], inorganic material [300010360], materials by composition [300212963], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
